            "subject": "Exit Interview SOP",
            "body_plain": "Standard exit interview procedure:\n\n1. Schedule exit interview 5 business days before the employee's last day.\n2. Send calendar invite to employee and their manager.\n3. Email the employee a pre-interview questionnaire.\n4. Update the tracker Status to 'Interview Scheduled'.\n5. If the last day has already passed, mark as 'Missed - Schedule ASAP' and email HR Director (hr-director@company.example.com).\n\n- HR Manager",
