            "subject": "Re: Exit Interview Process - Update for Involuntary Separations",
            "body_plain": "Team,\n\nUpdated guidance: For involuntary separations, do NOT schedule exit interviews. These employees should be marked as 'Exempt - Involuntary' in the tracker. Only voluntary departures get exit interviews.\n\nThis overrides the general SOP for this specific case.\n\n- HR Director",
